cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.GT

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper is about a deductive system for a fragment of CoL and program extraction from proofs. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses program extraction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as CoL is a theory of interactive computation and the paper discusses extracting winning strategies. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as CoL is a theory of computability and the paper discusses computational problems. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as CoL understands computational problems as games played by two players.
